# FormCast is a Windows-only project (targets TCC v36+ on Windows). All
# text files are stored and checked out as CRLF so every consumer and
# every Windows-native parser (cmd.exe, powershell.exe, tcc.exe, older
# Windows text editors) gets native line endings without conversion.
# Aligns with the .editorconfig end_of_line = crlf policy.

* text=auto eol=crlf

# Explicit binary markers. Git auto-detects binary via NUL bytes, but
# these extensions are unambiguous and benefit from being pinned.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.dll binary
*.exe binary
*.pdb binary
*.lib binary
